{"about_the_game":"FurBalls Racing is a fast-paced, platforming racing game that's silly and surprisingly challenging! Whether you want to have a party with friends or try to get perfect runs on every stage, FurBalls Racing is fun for all kinds of players!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1962490/extras/preview.gif?t=1675809841\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as over a dozen unique squishy FurBalls, each one with different attributes!<br></li><li>Roll, wall jump, spin drift, and take creative shortcuts as you rush towards the finish line!<br></li><li>Eat cheese, then use it to... shoot poop?... at your opponents...<br></li><li>Play locally with up to four players in split screen!<br></li><li>Race against up to fifteen CPU players in Grand Prix!<br></li><li>Record and face your own best times as ghosts in Time Trials mode, where you can also race against challenging staff ghosts!<br></li><li>Try to get medals on every stage to unlock more playable characters!<br></li><li>Play online to race against distant friends or anyone else!<br></li><li>Challenging unlockable content, secrets, crazy shortcuts, and hidden advanced game mechanics for speedrunners and other hardcore players!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Graduation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1962490/793a6290540098b0c6760da7b2d97cc99d0941d6.jpg"},{"name":"Quick Learner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1962490/741654daee94e5b347f1f1e0c2c8238bf753dfe3.jpg"},{"name":"Rapid Roller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1962490/5538d4f592debc431a48c375db6dce65eba026c5.jpg"},{"name":"Dizzy Dasher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1962490/b03b744bea4e29446fa5bc7ba75dcbb639bede7f.jpg"},{"name":"Fuzzy Champ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm